node.text:
I have loved sharing my ongoing skin journey with you all. I am so grateful to continue to go in the right direction after finding out the root causes!

I have goals of focusing on overall texture, more hydration, and overall glow. I am going to take you babes on the journey of finishing this entire bottle of PITERA™ Essence from @skii . Along the way I will be giving my feedback and how my skin overall feels with this product! Excited to share my journey. #MyPITERAStory #skiipartner

node.text:
Not being able to workout for quite some time really makes you appreciate being able to move your body.
-
Little glimpse from my full body & abs on @joinform ! Link in bio!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by S A M I  C L A R K E on August 09, 2021 tagging @dailydrills. May be an image of 1 person, standing and indoor.

node.text:
Your girl is back, so had to bring the mirror pic back too, you know?
-
I am very excited to get back into my workouts and my routines! You know you missed your routine when you enjoyed drinking celery juice this morning… Happy Monday Fam, sending everyone the best vibes for a great week!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by S A M I  C L A R K E on August 03, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and indoor.

node.text:
What a day yesterday! So grateful for everyone who signed up and joined the community @joinform ! Your girl must have gotten too excited yesterday… woke up needing some extra rest and slow pace movement today. 
-
Can’t wait to bring you babes new workouts every week, the workouts that I fell in love with and changed me from the inside out!!
